    </p>
    <a href="#features" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Learn More</a>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="features" class="py-5">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="text-center mb-4">Features</h2>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title">URL Shortening</h5>
            <p class="card-text">
              Automatically generate the shortest possible URL for easy sharing
              on any platform.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title">Custom URLs</h5>
            <p class="card-text">
              Create custom, branded URLs that reflect your brand or content.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title">QR Code Generation</h5>
            <p class="card-text">
              Generate and download QR codes for your shortened URLs to use in
              promotional materials.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="faqs" class="py-5 bg-light">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="text-center mb-4">FAQs</h2>
    <div class="accordion" id="faqsAccordion">
      <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingOne">
          <button
            class="accordion-button"
            type="button"
            data-bs-toggle="collapse"
            data-bs-target="#collapseOne"
            aria-expanded="true"
            aria-controls="collapseOne"
          >
            What is Scissor?
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div
          id="collapseOne"
          class="accordion-collapse collapse show"
          aria-labelledby="headingOne"
          data-bs-parent="#faqsAccordion"
        >
          <div class="accordion-body">
            Scissor is a tool that shortens URLs to make them easier to share,
            with additional features like custom URLs and QR code generation.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingTwo">
          <button
            class="accordion-button collapsed"
            type="button"
            data-bs-toggle="collapse"
            data-bs-target="#collapseTwo"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controls="collapseTwo"
          >
            How can I create a custom URL?
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div
          id="collapseTwo"
          class="accordion-collapse collapse"
          aria-labelledby="headingTwo"
          data-bs-parent="#faqsAccordion"
        >
          <div class="accordion-body">
            You can create a custom URL by choosing your own custom domain name
            and customizing the URL to reflect your brand or content.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="accordion-item">
        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingThree">
          <button
            class="accordion-button collapsed"
            type="button"
            data-bs-toggle="collapse"
            data-bs-target="#collapseThree"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controls="collapseThree"
          >
            What analytics does Scissor provide?
          </button>
        </h2>
        <div
          id="collapseThree"
          class="accordion-collapse collapse"
          aria-labelledby="headingThree"
        >
          <div class="accordion-body">
            Scissor provides basic analytics that allow you to track the
            performance of your shortened URLs, including click counts and
            geographic location of clicks.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
